  "texts": [
    "It is likely that underuse vary depending on the test concerned [133][134][135].",
    "Future studies assessing consequences of reducing underuse are needed.Several limitations of this review deserve mention.",
    "Although comprehensive, our literature search was not systematic.",
    "We did not systematically evaluate the quality of studies, or their potential biases.",
    "Yet, a 2015 systematic review emphasizes the poor quality of interventional studies in the general setting [23]."
  ]
